comments: Bitadze (IND) makes incidental contact with Morris Sr. (LAC) arm following the release of his jump shot attempt.
Bitadze (IND) legally contests Batum's (LAC) shot attempt near the rim.
Jackson (LAC) briefly applies his forearm to LeVert's (IND) front during the drive. LeVert moves through the marginal contact and continues his drive.
Zubac (LAC) establishes a legal position in LeVert's (IND) path and he absorbs the marginal contact during the pick.
Bitadze (IND) legally contests Jackson (LAC) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Coffey (LAC) makes incidental contact with LeVert's (IND) arm following the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
LeVert (IND) extends his leg into Jackson's (LAC) path and the contact that occurs affects Jackson's SQBR.
Brissett (IND) jumps from point A to point B and his arm delivers contact to Jackson's (LAC) head during the driving shot attempt.
LeVert (IND) leads with his elbow and he delivers contact to Batum's (LAC) head/face which affects his ability to defend the driving shot attempt.
Holiday (IND) commits a take foul on Jackson (LAC).
Sabonis (IND) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Coffey's (LAC) path and marginal contact occurs during the off ball screen,
Duarte (IND) commits a take foul on Jackson (LAC).
Batum (LAC) wraps two hands around Sabonis' (IND) body during the pick. The contact affects Sabonis' ability to disengage and move freely.
